726965f-a.text:
Jamaica, Queens: Shown are three views across a sparsely settled section of North Jamaica, known as "Jamaica Hillcrest.' The area lies between Grand Central Parkway and Union Turnpike, east of 168th Street. The point of vantage is 168th Street and 82nd Avenue, view 1 being northeast, view 2 north, and view 3 east across the
Hillcrest Golf Course.
P. L. Sperr  March 31, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
